# Plan 14: Video Integration & Player

## Goal
Create the "Videos" page and admin management for videos.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/videos/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Create `app/admin/videos/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Implement a `VideoCard` component with a play overlay.
- [ ] Create a video player modal that supports YouTube/Vimeo embeds and native HTML5 video.
- [ ] Fetch videos from the database.
- [ ] Implement video management in the admin panel (add links, upload thumbnails).
